# CODEOWNERS
# Each line defines a file pattern and the owner(s) responsible for reviewing changes.
# Owners are automatically requested for review when a pull request modifies matching files.
# More specific rules override broader ones.
# Documentation: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# ---------------------------------------------------------
# Global owner — reviews all changes by default
# ---------------------------------------------------------
*   @cmonrel

# ---------------------------------------------------------
# Source code
# ---------------------------------------------------------
/src/   @cmonrel
# /src/   @cmonrel @new-collaborator

# ---------------------------------------------------------
# Configuration files
# ---------------------------------------------------------
*.config.*      @cmonrel
*.json          @cmonrel
# *.config.*    @cmonrel @new-collaborator

# ---------------------------------------------------------
# Documentation
# ---------------------------------------------------------
/docs/          @cmonrel
*.md            @cmonrel
# /docs/        @cmonrel @new-collaborator

# ---------------------------------------------------------
# CI/CD and GitHub settings
# ---------------------------------------------------------
/.github/       @cmonrel
# /.github/     @cmonrel @new-collaborator
  
